                <note rend="inline" type="source">825.796/25</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                            <gloss type="to">Pan American Airways, Inc.</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1928-10-13">
                            <hi rend="italic">October 13, 1928</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>
                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Sirs</hi>: With reference to your project for supplying air
                    mail service from the United States to the southernmost part of Chile,
                    concerning which the Department informed the American Embassy at Santiago some
                    time ago, I have to inform you that the American Ambassador to Chile has now
                    telegraphed that he would be pleased to receive any pertinent information
                    regarding the Chilean section of the proposed air mail service which would
                    facilitate his obtaining from the Chilean Government more precise indication as
                    to the extent of that Government’s probable cooperation and facilities.</p>
                <p>In order that the Department may reply by telegraph to the Ambassador, I shall be
                    pleased to receive any information you can give me regarding the latest
                    developments with regard to this project.</p>
                <p>I am [etc.]</p>
                <closer>For the Secretary of State:<lb/>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Francis White</hi>
                    </signed>
                    <lb/>
                    <hi rend="italic">Assistant Secretary</hi>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
